/> Are there only seven qualities that befit the righteous and no other?<br
/> The number seven is a symbol of completeness, just as Creation was completed in seven days. Each of the qualities listed here is representative of a type of quality and there are seven types altogether. All other good qualities are included in these seven types or are similar to them.</p><p>Dedicated to Carolyn McLarge</p><p><p><a
